posting_body: ['3 Bedroom  2 Bathroom | 1276 - 1538 sq ft | $2429 - $2558/Month', 'The Cielo Apartments', '5951 University Ave NE', 'Fridley, MN 55432', 'show contact info', 'Description:', 'The Cielo is proudly managed by Peak Living.', 'At Peak Living, our mission is to provide the highest quality property management services in the industry.', 'We achieve this through our greatest asset; our people.', 'Our on-site and regional management teams offer unsurpassed customer service and local expertise for those living at our properties and for our clients.', 'Our experiences and entrepreneurial spirit mean that we understand that no two buildings or clients are the same, and as such, flexibility and adaptability are key to achieving investment goals.', 'Through the use of the latest technologies, Peak Living is able to provide exceptional accounting/reporting as well as industry-leading portal functionality for prospective and current residents, including digital lease signing, online work order submission, and online payments.', 'Apartment Amenities:', '● Air Conditioner', '● Bright Open-Concept Floor Plans', '● Carpeting', '● Ceiling Fan In Select Units', '● Dishwasher', '● Efficient Appliances', '● Kitchen Pantry In Select Units', '● Microwave', '● Private Patio or Balcony Space', 'In Select Units', '● Separate Dining Area In Select Units', 'Our Residents Enjoy:', '● 24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', '● Conference Room', '● Controlled Access', '● Elevator', '● Fitness Center', '● Free Weights', '● Game Room', '● On-Site Maintenance', '● On-Site Management', '● Playground', '● Community Room & Lounges', '● Heated Parking Garage', '● Managed Parcel Storage System', '● Professionally Designed and Maintained Landscape', '● Resident Services Portal with Online Payment & Maintenance Request Options', '● Study Area', '● Walking Paths & Grilling Pavilions', 'Additional Details:', 'Deposit: Call', 'Terms: Variable', 'Pets: Pets Welcome!', 'Non-aggressive breeds accepted.', 'Weight Restrictions may apply.', 'Please see the office for fees & other details!', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>/', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'D4816CB5C81C40']
